1. DIRETTA HOST SDK DEPENDENCY

   This software requires the Diretta Host SDK, which is proprietary software
   owned by Yu Harada and is NOT included in this repository.

   - Diretta Host SDK Website: https://www.diretta.link
   - The SDK can be downloaded from: https://www.diretta.link/hostsdk.html
   - The Diretta Host SDK is licensed separately by Yu Harada

   PERSONAL USE ONLY: The Diretta Host SDK is provided for PERSONAL,
   NON-COMMERCIAL USE ONLY. Commercial use of the Diretta Host SDK requires
   separate licensing from Yu Harada.

   This software (excluding the Diretta SDK) is provided under the MIT License
   above, but its practical use is subject to the Diretta SDK license terms.

2. DIRETTASYNC COMPONENT

   The DirettaSync component is derived from DirettaRendererUPnP v2.0.0,
   originally developed by Dominique COMET and licensed under MIT.

   Original repository: https://github.com/cometdom/DirettaRendererUPnP

   Contributors to DirettaSync:
   - Dominique COMET (Original Work)
   - SwissMontainsBear (Modifications)
   - Leeeanh (SIMD and PCM Optimizations)

3. SQUEEZELITE DEPENDENCY

   This software launches Squeezelite as a separate process. Squeezelite is
   licensed under GPL v3 by Adrian Smith and Ralph Irving.

   Squeezelite repository: https://github.com/ralph-irving/squeezelite

   Note: This wrapper communicates with Squeezelite via standard I/O pipes
   and does not link against or include Squeezelite code directly.

